---
/* src/components/Sheer-elegance/Specifications.astro */
---

<section class="bg-[#131313] py-24 px-8 border-b border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16">
    
    <div class="lg:w-1/3">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold text-white mb-6">Especificaciones Técnicas</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 font-['Inter'] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Diseñadas para durar, fabricadas con los más altos estándares de calidad y ensambladas con precisión para los hogares de Zipaquirá y Sabana Centro.
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-[#0e0e0e] p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-lg group hover:border-[#dcef42]/30 transition-colors duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#dcef42] text-3xl transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">verified</span>
          <div>
            <h5 class="text-white font-bold font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-lg">Garantía Certificada</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/60 font-['Inter'] mt-1">5 años en mecanismos y tejidos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lg:w-2/3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8">
      
      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-4 hover:border-[#dcef42]/50 transition-colors duration-300">
        <span class="text-xs font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-[#dcef42] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Material</span>
        <p class="text-xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold mt-2">100% Poliéster de Alta Tenacidad</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-4 hover:border-[#dcef42]/50 transition-colors duration-300">
        <span class="text-xs font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-[#dcef42] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Ancho de Franja</span>
        <p class="text-xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold mt-2">Desde 55mm hasta 90mm</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-4 hover:border-[#dcef42]/50 transition-colors duration-300">
        <span class="text-xs font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-[#dcef42] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Accionamiento</span>
        <p class="text-xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold mt-2">Manual (Cordón/Cadena) o Motorizado</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-4 hover:border-[#dcef42]/50 transition-colors duration-300">
        <span class="text-xs font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-[#dcef42] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Instalación</span>
        <p class="text-xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold mt-2">Pared, Techo o Marco de Ventana</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-4 hover:border-[#dcef42]/50 transition-colors duration-300">
        <span class="text-xs font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-[#dcef42] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Cabezal</span>
        <p class="text-xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold mt-2">Perfil de Aluminio en Colores Coordinados</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="border-b border-white/10 pb-4 hover:border-[#dcef42]/50 transition-colors duration-300">
        <span class="text-xs font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-[#dcef42] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Mantenimiento</span>
        <p class="text-xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold mt-2">Tejido Anti-estático (Repele el Polvo)</p>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>